{"type":null,"faqId":45112,"title":"蓝牙耳机与手机配对，可以配对成功，但是不自动连接，需要手动连接怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">蓝牙耳机距离过远断开，部分耳机会退出可被连接模式造成不能自动连接的情况，此时需要配对过的手机发起连接促使耳机进入可被连接模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请用户尝试：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 在手机上解除配对，重启耳机和手机后，重新从蓝牙设置中配对设备进行连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 建议使用市场上使用量较大的蓝牙耳机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 建议您通过华为官方网站、论坛等，搜索下类似问题的解决办法。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"613","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409589000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":16,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙耳机不自动连接","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}